128
00:11:10,870 --> 00:11:12,460
Passed.

129
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:17,060
- Han.
- We're up next!

130
00:11:21,670 --> 00:11:23,910
I choose Spirit Beast Mountain!

131
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:43,700
