139
00:12:17,912 --> 00:12:21,300
Are we rogue cultivators doomed to always be trampled by them?

140
00:12:21,300 --> 00:12:22,260
I can't just swallow this!

141
00:12:22,260 --> 00:12:24,500
They keep talking about the same stuff.

142
00:12:24,500 --> 00:12:27,690
Still, there might be another way.

143
00:12:27,690 --> 00:12:29,322
