144
00:12:29,322 --> 00:12:32,340
But... I'll need everyone's help.

145
00:12:32,340 --> 00:12:33,790
What plan, Sir?

146
00:12:33,790 --> 00:12:35,480
We can't wait. Just spit it out!

147
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:38,450
- Sir, please tell us!
- No more teasing.

148
00:12:38,450 --> 00:12:42,100
Mr. Wan, if we run into each other on the arena,

149
00:12:42,100 --> 00:12:44,130
