150
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:47,740
Sir, you're really joking.

151
00:12:47,740 --> 00:12:51,150
Your cultivation is way above mine.
Of course I'd lose.

152
00:12:51,860 --> 00:12:53,770
Then...

153
00:12:54,570 --> 00:12:57,000
what if I lend you this horsetail whisk?

154
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:59,180
It's a mid-grade artifact.

155
00:12:59,180 --> 00:13:02,870
Well... I might have a 50-50 chance.

156
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:07,360
What if I also lend you this treasure?

157
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:12,272
Then... maybe... Oh, I'd have a 70 percent chance!

158
00:13:12,272 --> 00:13:13,630
Great.

159
00:13:13,630 --> 00:13:16,890
In the cultivation world, battles aren't just about power.

160
00:13:16,890 --> 00:13:21,170
They also rely on artifacts, talismans, and pills.

161
00:13:21,170 --> 00:13:22,460
In terms of strength and techniques,

162
00:13:22,460 --> 00:13:24,920
we can't compete
with those arrogant clan disciples.

163
00:13:24,920 --> 00:13:29,810
But there's one thing we have
that they don't, unity.

164
00:13:29,810 --> 00:13:32,030
If our Azure Vein Society
had a hundred rogue cultivators,

165
00:13:32,030 --> 00:13:35,050
and each one was willing to contribute a treasure,

166
00:13:35,050 --> 00:13:38,140
then we'd have a hundred treasures in our hands!

167
00:13:38,140 --> 00:13:39,780
With that many treasures,

168
00:13:39,780 --> 00:13:42,950
even if we're facing Foundation Establishment cultivators,

169
00:13:42,950 --> 00:13:44,850
we might still stand a chance.

170
00:13:44,850 --> 00:13:47,410
Absolutely!

171
00:13:47,410 --> 00:13:51,460
I'm willing to lend my mid-grade whisk
for everyone to use.

172
00:13:51,460 --> 00:13:53,180
Qing Wen...

173
00:13:53,180 --> 00:13:55,620
Since I brought this up,
it's only right I set the example.

174
00:13:55,620 --> 00:13:56,900
I've said before.

175
00:13:56,900 --> 00:13:58,390
The reason I founded the Azure Vein Society

176
00:13:58,390 --> 00:14:01,260
was to build a world
where all cultivators are equal.

177
00:14:01,260 --> 00:14:03,140
We'll show those clan kids

178
00:14:03,140 --> 00:14:05,530
that rogue cultivators like us
are no less than any of them!

179
00:14:05,530 --> 00:14:06,720
- Yes!
- Right!

180
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:08,440
- We're not weaker than them!
- They're nothing special!

181
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:10,810
See? You can't go wrong following this sir!

182
00:14:10,810 --> 00:14:13,110
I know, even with all these treasures,

183
00:14:13,110 --> 00:14:16,750
not everyone here will walk away victorious.

184
00:14:16,750 --> 00:14:19,790
But as long as we give it our all,
even if we lose,

185
00:14:19,790 --> 00:14:21,770
we'll make those clan disciples see

186
00:14:21,770 --> 00:14:23,840
we rogue cultivators won't be pushed around!

187
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:25,600
We won't be pushed around!

188
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:26,790
We won't be pushed around!

189
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:30,500
Sir, even though I lack talent, I still want to contribute something!

190
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:32,020
Good!

191
00:14:32,020 --> 00:14:34,900
Then, those who want to help, come with me!

192
00:14:34,900 --> 00:14:36,030
All right!

193
00:14:36,030 --> 00:14:37,380
- Let's go!
- Yes!

194
00:14:37,380 --> 00:14:39,060
I'll contribute what I can!

195
00:14:39,550 --> 00:14:41,800
- Take mine!
- Here you go!

196
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:44,890
- Take mine!
- So that's their plan all along.

197
00:14:51,570 --> 00:14:54,820
Mr. Han, would you be willing to help?

198
00:14:57,570 --> 00:14:59,401
After hearing what you said,

199
00:14:59,401 --> 00:15:03,160
I've lost interest in joining the Seven Sects.

200
00:15:03,160 --> 00:15:07,390
I won't join the tournament at Tianwu Arena.

201
00:15:08,450 --> 00:15:11,830
My friend, this is our best chance to make a name for ourselves!

202
00:15:11,830 --> 00:15:13,960
- Yeah, a golden opportunity!
- Totally!

203
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:16,350
- Do your part!
-  Looks like I can't leave today

204
00:15:16,350 --> 00:15:17,860
without bleeding a little.

205
00:15:17,860 --> 00:15:20,840
If you've got treasures, bring them out and share!

206
00:15:21,650 --> 00:15:23,200
All right.

207
00:15:24,500 --> 00:15:29,020
I happened to come
across a restorative pill.

208
00:15:29,020 --> 00:15:30,910
I planned to keep it for myself.

209
00:15:30,910 --> 00:15:32,550
But under the circumstances,

210
00:15:33,170 --> 00:15:34,750
I'll share it with everyone.

211
00:15:34,750 --> 00:15:37,620
Much appreciated, Mr.!

212
00:15:37,620 --> 00:15:39,910
That's a good one.

213
00:15:40,650 --> 00:15:42,820
Ugh, my stomach hurts.

214
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:44,810
I need to take a quick break.

215
00:15:44,810 --> 00:15:46,920
You guys keep chatting.

216
00:15:56,690 --> 00:15:58,270
Han!

217
00:16:02,470 --> 00:16:05,730
You... You're fine?

218
00:16:07,390 --> 00:16:09,110
I'm fine now.

219
00:16:12,380 --> 00:16:16,620
Xiao Shan, are you here to talk me
into joining the Azure Vein Society?

220
00:16:16,620 --> 00:16:18,170
Of course not.

221
00:16:18,170 --> 00:16:20,740
But, aren't you planning to join
the Tianwu Arena tournament

222
00:16:20,740 --> 00:16:22,780
and win yourself a Foundation Pill?

223
00:16:23,570 --> 00:16:27,590
The Seven Sects are great, but I gotta stay alive first.

224
00:16:27,590 --> 00:16:30,770
I knew it, Han. You're not one to go in blind.

225
00:16:32,790 --> 00:16:36,080
Well, you weren't joining the fight.

226
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:38,610
So why'd you still share your treasure?

227
00:16:38,610 --> 00:16:40,890
Just trying to win us rogues a little respect.

228
00:16:40,890 --> 00:16:42,510
Xiao Shan.

229
00:16:43,870 --> 00:16:47,380
I can't shake the feeling that those guys aren't as simple as they look.

230
00:16:47,380 --> 00:16:50,550
With your kind of naivety, you'll get burned.

231
00:16:50,550 --> 00:16:53,030
No way! All rogue cultivators are one big family!

232
00:16:53,030 --> 00:16:55,180
You're overthinking it, Han.

233
00:16:58,320 --> 00:17:01,630
With what we saved up earlier, we've got 38 artifacts now.

234
00:17:01,630 --> 00:17:06,020
Qing Wen, why not take all this and run off now?

235
00:17:06,020 --> 00:17:10,030
No. The barrier at the Tainan
Bazaar won't lift until the tournament is over.

236
00:17:10,030 --> 00:17:12,240
We can't leave yet.

237
00:17:13,570 --> 00:17:17,630
If those rogue cultivators give up
their treasures willingly, that's ideal.

238
00:17:17,630 --> 00:17:20,270
If not...

239
00:17:20,270 --> 00:17:23,460
Don't worry, Sir!
If they won't, I'll be the first to...

240
00:17:23,460 --> 00:17:25,840
Yeah, we won't spare them!

241
00:17:28,100 --> 00:17:29,550
How many times do I have to say it?

242
00:17:29,550 --> 00:17:32,710
Stop talking about fighting
and killing all the time!

243
00:17:35,750 --> 00:17:37,250
Get up.

244
00:17:39,960 --> 00:17:41,270
Yes, Sir.

245
00:17:41,270 --> 00:17:43,160
