246
00:17:51,550 --> 00:17:53,250
Li!

247
00:17:57,320 --> 00:17:59,050
I finally found you!

248
00:17:59,050 --> 00:18:00,320
What is it now?

249
00:18:00,320 --> 00:18:02,380
I've got more talismans here.

250
00:18:02,380 --> 00:18:05,800
