252
00:18:12,910 --> 00:18:14,790
These are offensive.

253
00:18:14,790 --> 00:18:16,860
These ones are defensive.

254
00:18:16,860 --> 00:18:18,770
This Vajra Talisman is amazing!

255
00:18:18,770 --> 00:18:22,720
It can block a full-force strike
from a tenth-level Qi Refiner!

256
00:18:22,720 --> 00:18:23,650
What about this one?

257
00:18:23,650 --> 00:18:25,450
This is a Thunderfire Talisman.

258
00:18:25,450 --> 00:18:28,380
It hits with both lightning and fire at once.

259
00:18:28,380 --> 00:18:30,110
Look!

260
00:18:33,240 --> 00:18:37,320
