261
00:18:37,860 --> 00:18:39,080
That's weird.

262
00:18:39,080 --> 00:18:41,800
I followed the book's instructions exactly.

263
00:18:42,790 --> 00:18:46,060
Li, how about these two?

264
00:18:46,060 --> 00:18:48,860
I guarantee they're top quality.

265
00:18:48,860 --> 00:18:51,450
These two...

266
00:18:51,450 --> 00:18:55,090
Miss Han, why do you need pills so urgently?

267
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:58,290
I want to cure my brother's illness.

268
00:19:00,170 --> 00:19:06,130
Sorry, but your talismans
are not very useful to me.

269
00:19:06,130 --> 00:19:13,610
Still, if you've got cinnabar and talisman paper, I might be interested.

270
00:19:13,610 --> 00:19:15,910
You want to make talismans yourself?

271
00:19:17,350 --> 00:19:20,000
Then you'll definitely need this!

272
00:19:22,790 --> 00:19:25,170
This one is a Golden Bamboo Brush.

273
00:19:25,170 --> 00:19:28,250
The tip is made from the tail hair
of a Level Two demon beast.

274
00:19:28,250 --> 00:19:31,780
The shaft is forged from black iron
mixed with refined gold.

275
00:19:31,780 --> 00:19:35,860
It was crafted using secret techniques
by a Foundation Establishment cultivator.

276
00:19:35,860 --> 00:19:39,190
This is a must-have tool for talisman making!

277
00:19:49,970 --> 00:19:51,830
A true rarity!

278
00:19:51,830 --> 00:19:53,410
You're really selling it to me?

279
00:19:53,410 --> 00:19:57,170
Honestly, it's a family heirloom.

280
00:19:57,170 --> 00:20:02,160
But as you can see,
I'm terrible at making talismans.

281
00:20:02,160 --> 00:20:06,870
So this brush is pretty much wasted on me.

282
00:20:06,870 --> 00:20:08,620
How much are you asking?

283
00:20:09,210 --> 00:20:12,620
Two bottles of pills. How about that?

284
00:20:12,620 --> 00:20:16,780
I'll even throw in these talismans, ink, and this Talisman Compendium.

285
00:20:22,589 --> 00:20:24,249
Deal.

286
00:20:33,310 --> 00:20:35,080
Li!

287
00:20:36,830 --> 00:20:38,620
I also have a Clear Stream Note.

288
00:20:38,620 --> 00:20:41,070
It's got all sorts of funny stories
from the cultivation world.

289
00:20:41,070 --> 00:20:42,070
I've read it already.

290
00:20:42,070 --> 00:20:45,450
If you get bored, maybe it'll help pass the time.

291
00:20:53,690 --> 00:20:57,190
I was hoping to learn more anyway. Thanks.

292
00:21:12,650 --> 00:21:16,672
"Anyone holding an Ascension
Token can skip testing and join a sect."

293
00:21:16,672 --> 00:21:19,425
"He may even get a Foundation Pill."

294
00:21:19,425 --> 00:21:21,795
What's an Ascension Token?

295
00:22:05,490 --> 00:22:09,210
Han! Let's go check out the Tianwu Arena!

296
00:22:09,210 --> 00:22:12,820
I heard the sects have prepared
a bunch of rewards this time

297
00:22:12,820 --> 00:22:15,250
to attract more participants.

298
00:22:15,250 --> 00:22:20,770
The winner gets a Foundation Pill
and a ton of gems and techniques.

299
00:22:21,970 --> 00:22:27,620
Xiao Shan, I got a book
with all sorts of cultivation oddities.

300
00:22:27,620 --> 00:22:29,070
Not sure if they're true.

301
00:22:29,070 --> 00:22:30,340
Want to check it out together?

302
00:22:30,340 --> 00:22:31,900
Sure!

303
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:35,050
Come over.

304
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:45,430
Clear Stream Note?

305
00:22:53,160 --> 00:22:55,200
What's this?

306
00:22:55,200 --> 00:23:00,080
Looks like a token from some sect.

307
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:03,590
That's not just any token.

308
00:23:03,590 --> 00:23:06,040
Look at the writing on it.

309
00:23:08,750 --> 00:23:11,820
Ascension Token...

310
00:23:11,820 --> 00:23:15,450
Ascension Token? What's that?

311
00:23:17,480 --> 00:23:20,892
The Ascension Token is for...

312
00:23:20,892 --> 00:23:23,110
They say...

313
00:23:23,780 --> 00:23:28,780
Well, I heard, if you hold an Ascension Token,

314
00:23:28,780 --> 00:23:31,700
you don't have to fight, don't have to take the spirit root test,

315
00:23:31,700 --> 00:23:33,890
you get straight into any of the Seven Sects.

316
00:23:33,890 --> 00:23:35,310
Is that true?

317
00:23:35,310 --> 00:23:37,000
Nonsense!

318
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:40,070
If that were true, everyone would be fighting over this token.

319
00:23:40,070 --> 00:23:42,570
Who'd bother risking their lives
at the tournament?

320
00:23:43,540 --> 00:23:46,490
Exactly. Sounds like a made-up story.

321
00:23:52,750 --> 00:23:54,850
Grandmaster, you were right.

322
00:23:54,850 --> 00:23:59,250
Several clan disciples
have reported their tokens stolen.

323
00:24:00,480 --> 00:24:03,340
The Azure Vein Society never quit causing trouble,

324
00:24:03,340 --> 00:24:05,680
even hit during the entrance test.

325
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:08,280
What should we do now?

326
00:24:09,720 --> 00:24:13,000
So those rogue cultivators' missing
is really linked to them.

327
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:15,590
And now they're pinning it on the clan disciples.

328
00:24:15,590 --> 00:24:20,100
Once the Tianwu Arena tournament ends, let's arrest them all.

329
00:24:21,030 --> 00:24:22,700
Yes, Grandmaster.

330
00:24:44,970 --> 00:24:49,480
Looks like this Ascension Token
is tied to Yellow Maple Valley.

331
00:24:49,480 --> 00:24:51,060
Yellow Maple Valley...

332
00:24:51,060 --> 00:24:54,490
They say it's one of the top sects
among the Seven.

333
00:24:54,490 --> 00:24:56,900
What luck!

334
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:25,910
Nothing left to worry about now.

335
00:25:52,790 --> 00:25:54,830
Charging in knowing you'll lose?

336
00:25:54,830 --> 00:25:57,340
You think you're worthy of this Foundation Pill?

337
00:25:57,340 --> 00:26:00,110
I've waited for this day for decades.

338
00:26:00,110 --> 00:26:04,100
You clan kid, don't get cocky!

339
00:26:20,200 --> 00:26:21,830
Who is this Qing Wen?

340
00:26:21,830 --> 00:26:24,010
Why does he have so many treasures?

341
00:26:24,550 --> 00:26:27,270
Is Lu about to lose?

342
00:26:27,270 --> 00:26:29,980
No way. He's just about to win.

343
00:26:57,960 --> 00:27:00,820
Sir, you went easy on me.

344
00:27:14,680 --> 00:27:17,200
It's a test. Don't take it too far.

345
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:20,680
He already admitted defeat. Why try to kill him?

346
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:22,960
Grandmaster, please forgive me.

347
00:27:22,960 --> 00:27:26,820
I didn't realize he had already surrendered.

348
00:27:26,820 --> 00:27:28,380
You didn't realize

349
00:27:28,380 --> 00:27:31,440
or was it because your opponent
was just some nameless rogue cultivator,

350
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:33,660
and you didn't care?

351
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:38,640
Thank you, Grandmaster, for standing up
for us rogue cultivators!

352
00:27:38,640 --> 00:27:40,540
- Yes!
- Thank you for standing up for us!

353
00:27:40,540 --> 00:27:45,040
Please stand up for us! Please, we need your voice!

354
00:27:45,920 --> 00:27:48,780
I'm aware many rogue cultivators
have gone missing lately.

355
00:27:48,780 --> 00:27:51,550
Our Moonshadow Sect will get to the bottom of it.

356
00:27:51,550 --> 00:27:54,490
If anyone is found stirring up conflict
between rogues and clan disciples,

357
00:27:54,490 --> 00:27:56,960
disrupting the order of the cultivation world,

358
00:27:58,640 --> 00:28:01,040
I will not show mercy.

359
00:28:15,250 --> 00:28:18,710
Lu Ming Yuan wins! Receives one Foundation Pill!

360
00:28:18,710 --> 00:28:22,880
Senior Lu is amazing! You've got the Foundation Pill!

361
00:28:25,930 --> 00:28:29,480
A cultivator's strength
doesn't just depend on spirit roots,

362
00:28:29,480 --> 00:28:34,210
but also on artifacts, talismans, formations,
and pills.

363
00:28:34,210 --> 00:28:37,300
Use everything you've got, plan carefully before making a move.

364
00:28:37,300 --> 00:28:39,060
Lay low, then explode.

365
00:28:39,060 --> 00:28:43,432
Maybe this is the path meant for me.

366
00:28:43,432 --> 00:28:48,729
But in the face of overwhelming strength, all shortcuts are doomed to fail.

367
00:28:48,729 --> 00:28:51,830
- Congrats, Senior Lu!
- Congrats, Senior Lu!

368
00:28:55,550 --> 00:28:58,440
He got into Yellow Maple Valley too?

369
00:28:58,440 --> 00:29:01,040
What are the odds!

370
00:29:09,030 --> 00:29:13,010
Just one step...I was just one step from victory!

371
00:29:13,010 --> 00:29:17,110
Qing Wen, that guy's a genius with a variant spirit root after all.

372
00:29:17,110 --> 00:29:19,450
No need to go head-to-head with him.

373
00:29:19,450 --> 00:29:21,620
We failed this time, but there's always next time.

374
00:29:21,620 --> 00:29:24,660
Next time? You think chances like this come easy?

375
00:29:24,660 --> 00:29:27,760
I told you,
we rogue cultivators are one big family.

376
00:29:27,760 --> 00:29:28,890
Don't take it so hard.

377
00:29:28,890 --> 00:29:30,520
- Enough already.
- You're making my heart ache.

378
00:29:30,520 --> 00:29:32,040
Hey...

379
00:29:38,340 --> 00:29:40,980
Listen, everyone. Don't be so down.

380
00:29:40,980 --> 00:29:44,400
I heard if you find a certain item,

381
00:29:44,400 --> 00:29:48,000
you can skip the tournament and still get into the Seven Sects.

382
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:50,480
- What item?
- What is it?

383
00:29:51,200 --> 00:29:54,412
I think it's called...the Ascension Token!

384
00:29:54,412 --> 00:29:56,650
Ascension Token?

385
00:29:56,650 --> 00:29:58,920
Ascension Token?

386
00:29:58,920 --> 00:30:01,400
Sir, I was about to ask you.

387
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:02,620
Do you know about the Ascension Token?

388
00:30:02,620 --> 00:30:04,862
The Ascension Token was
created by the Seven Sects.

389
00:30:04,862 --> 00:30:08,580
It was meant to reward
cultivation families who made great contributions.

390
00:30:08,580 --> 00:30:10,210
It could be passed down for generations.

391
00:30:10,210 --> 00:30:13,490
They say anyone who holds one can join any sect

392
00:30:13,490 --> 00:30:17,100
without taking the test
and even get a Foundation Pill.

393
00:30:17,100 --> 00:30:19,720
A Foundation Pill?

394
00:30:19,720 --> 00:30:25,200
No test and a Foundation Pill? That's amazing.

395
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:29,160
But this thing hasn't shown up for centuries.

396
00:30:29,160 --> 00:30:31,240
How do you even know about it?

397
00:30:31,790 --> 00:30:37,092
I didn't know, but Han...He read about it in a book.

398
00:30:37,640 --> 00:30:39,570
He asked you directly?

399
00:30:40,930 --> 00:30:46,340
No... Not really. We were just casually chatting.

400
00:30:46,340 --> 00:30:49,060
Where's Han Li now? Why isn't he here?

401
00:30:49,060 --> 00:30:50,920
Han Li...

402
00:30:51,620 --> 00:30:54,150
He's not around.

403
00:30:54,680 --> 00:30:58,050
Weren't you always with him?

404
00:30:58,780 --> 00:31:02,240
I don't really know him that well. I think he already left.

405
00:31:02,240 --> 00:31:04,480
He left?

406
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:08,210
But the barrier's still active. Where could he go?

407
00:31:08,210 --> 00:31:11,010
He... I...

408
00:31:16,640 --> 00:31:19,870
My stomach hurts!
I need a bathroom break!

409
00:31:21,750 --> 00:31:24,730
Why'd he run off? Is it really stomach pain?

410
00:31:24,730 --> 00:31:26,790
You buying it?

411
00:31:30,550 --> 00:31:34,170
Looks like this trip to the Tainan Bazaar
wasn't for nothing.

412
00:31:34,170 --> 00:31:37,620
These treasures
will really help my cultivation later on.

413
00:31:46,030 --> 00:31:47,960
So what if I have a fake spirit root?

414
00:31:47,960 --> 00:31:51,010
With this Ascension Token, I've got nothing to worry about!

415
00:32:14,880 --> 00:32:16,480
I'll just stay hidden till morning.

416
00:32:16,480 --> 00:32:21,480
Once the barrier lifts, I'll head straight to Yellow Maple Valley.

417
00:32:24,750 --> 00:32:27,940
He's there! Hurry!

418
00:32:28,640 --> 00:32:32,540
Stop! Stop running!

419
00:32:32,540 --> 00:32:34,800
Get him! Stop!

420
00:32:38,960 --> 00:32:42,700
Stop! He's there! Quick!

421
00:33:07,880 --> 00:33:10,350
Han! Han!

422
00:33:17,030 --> 00:33:21,010
Han!

423
00:33:21,550 --> 00:33:23,350
Xiao Shan!

424
00:33:52,480 --> 00:33:54,900
Xiao Shan! What happened?

425
00:33:54,900 --> 00:33:57,790
Han... Run!

426
00:33:57,790 --> 00:34:00,770
Qing Wen and his men are bad guys...

427
00:34:01,240 --> 00:34:03,300
I'm sorry...

428
00:34:03,300 --> 00:34:07,520
I... I got you into trouble...

429
00:34:16,620 --> 00:34:20,010
The Ascension Token has been exposed.

430
00:34:29,590 --> 00:34:32,050
Han! Why are you running?

431
00:34:32,050 --> 00:34:34,490
Stay and have a drink with us!

432
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:13,970
Nowhere to run now, huh?

433
00:35:19,240 --> 00:35:21,830
You two, why are you after me?

434
00:35:21,830 --> 00:35:23,400
What do you think?

435
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:28,830
At this point, Han, you can drop the act.

436
00:35:29,590 --> 00:35:33,070
Han, you're being awfully selfish.

437
00:35:33,070 --> 00:35:38,750
You got a treasure like the Ascension Token, but won't even let us take a look?

438
00:35:38,750 --> 00:35:40,240
Ascension Token?

439
00:35:40,240 --> 00:35:41,550
What is that?

440
00:35:41,550 --> 00:35:43,450
Never heard of it!

441
00:35:43,450 --> 00:35:47,050
You're trying to rob and kill someone
in broad daylight.

442
00:35:47,050 --> 00:35:49,740
Aren't you afraid the Seven Sects' punishment?

443
00:35:50,590 --> 00:35:52,230
Enough talk.

444
00:35:52,230 --> 00:35:56,260
Take him down first, then search his body.

445
00:36:36,190 --> 00:36:38,110
Where did he go?

446
00:36:38,110 --> 00:36:39,590
Find him!

447
00:36:40,190 --> 00:36:42,150
This won't work if it keeps up.

448
00:36:42,150 --> 00:36:45,520
That Qing Wen guy is still hiding in the shadows.

449
00:36:48,300 --> 00:36:50,260
Han,

450
00:36:51,480 --> 00:36:53,790
I see you!

451
00:36:58,970 --> 00:37:00,800
Stop hiding!

452
00:37:00,800 --> 00:37:02,840
Come out!

453
00:37:11,970 --> 00:37:14,210
A high-grade artifact!

454
00:37:15,490 --> 00:37:18,860
Qing Wen! Help me!

455
00:37:18,860 --> 00:37:20,680
Qing Wen!

456
00:37:42,380 --> 00:37:44,390
I knew you'd show up!

457
00:37:45,091 --> 00:37:48,282
Wan Xiao Shan was killed by you?

458
00:37:48,282 --> 00:37:50,380
He was a good man.

459
00:37:50,380 --> 00:37:53,580
But good men die too.

460
00:37:53,580 --> 00:37:55,320
You lost your men too.

461
00:37:55,320 --> 00:37:57,110
Why didn't you save them?

462
00:37:57,110 --> 00:37:59,820
I had a feeling you had something up your sleeve.

463
00:37:59,820 --> 00:38:01,960
So I let them go first.

464
00:38:01,960 --> 00:38:04,010
Looks like I was right.

465
00:38:05,880 --> 00:38:07,760
I get it now.

466
00:38:07,760 --> 00:38:12,490
There are three of you
but only one Ascension Token.

467
00:38:14,740 --> 00:38:16,410
You're a clever guy.

468
00:38:16,410 --> 00:38:17,920
Ping Gu and I go way back.

469
00:38:17,920 --> 00:38:22,550
If this weren't about the path to ascension, I wouldn't have let her die.

470
00:38:24,590 --> 00:38:27,660
You really are a complete villain.

471
00:38:30,480 --> 00:38:36,590
Han... that Flying Sword Talisman is your last trick, right?

472
00:38:37,820 --> 00:38:39,420
What do you think?

473
00:39:03,780 --> 00:39:05,590
This is Tainan Valley!

474
00:39:05,590 --> 00:39:08,400
If you kill me here,
aren't you afraid you'll get caught?

475
00:39:08,400 --> 00:39:10,550
You showed up out of nowhere,
clearly up to no good.

476
00:39:10,550 --> 00:39:12,200
All I have to say is you snuck in here,

477
00:39:12,200 --> 00:39:14,990
killed Wan Xiao Shan, Wu Jiu Zhi, and Ping Gu.

478
00:39:14,990 --> 00:39:16,960
I'll kill you to avenge them.

479
00:39:16,960 --> 00:39:20,660
Do you think the other rogues will believe you
or believe me?

480
00:39:21,190 --> 00:39:22,550
Fine!

481
00:39:22,550 --> 00:39:25,670
Then, I'll use the token as bait.

482
00:39:25,670 --> 00:39:28,480
Whoever kills you, gets it!

483
00:39:28,480 --> 00:39:29,880
You!

484
00:40:24,090 --> 00:40:27,630
You'd throw your life away over a token?

485
00:40:27,630 --> 00:40:29,550
You're still young.

486
00:40:29,550 --> 00:40:33,520
You don't understand what this means
to us rogue cultivators...

487
00:40:46,590 --> 00:40:47,990
Who's there?

488
00:40:59,300 --> 00:41:01,740
So, you're Daoist Qing Wen?

489
00:41:03,900 --> 00:41:05,820
Looks like you're dying.

490
00:41:05,820 --> 00:41:09,750
But my master said you can't die just yet.

491
00:41:10,510 --> 00:41:14,840
Which means he'll have to die instead.

492
00:41:22,700 --> 00:41:23,960
What stage is that guy in?

493
00:41:23,960 --> 00:41:25,510
I can't even track his movements.

494
00:41:25,510 --> 00:41:27,440
If I get caught, I'm dead for sure.

495
00:41:27,440 --> 00:41:29,110
I have to run!

496
00:41:45,230 --> 00:41:47,510
Who are you, sir?

497
00:41:48,380 --> 00:41:51,710
You founded the Azure Vein Society?

498
00:41:52,410 --> 00:41:54,292
Interesting...

499
00:41:54,292 --> 00:41:55,930
I'm just trying to stay alive.

500
00:41:55,930 --> 00:41:58,470
That guy earlier had the real treasure.

501
00:41:58,470 --> 00:42:04,100
If you can spare me, I'll question him myself and hand over the treasure!

502
00:42:04,100 --> 00:42:06,460
Ascension Token?

503
00:42:07,630 --> 00:42:09,970
A crumb tossed by the Seven Sects.

504
00:42:09,970 --> 00:42:12,540
You call that a treasure?

505
00:42:14,320 --> 00:42:16,260
Are you interested...

506
00:42:16,960 --> 00:42:20,260
in becoming a Foundation Establishment cultivator?

507
00:42:20,260 --> 00:42:22,110
Foundation...

508
00:42:24,400 --> 00:42:28,230
Senior, if you can help me
step into the Foundation Establishment stage,

509
00:42:28,230 --> 00:42:31,680
I, Qing Wen, will give my life to repay you!

510
00:42:33,480 --> 00:42:34,592
Senior...

511
00:42:34,592 --> 00:42:40,070
Even on death's door,
you're still dreaming of that?

512
00:42:40,700 --> 00:42:42,880
Please, help me!

513
00:42:43,550 --> 00:42:45,410
Fine.

514
00:42:56,440 --> 00:42:58,220
I felt a dark aura!

